#: ../../manual/render/cycles/materials/displacement.rst:13
msgid ""
"To create displacement, connect a :doc:`Displacement "
"</render/cycles/nodes/types/vector/displacement>` or :doc:`Vector "
"Displacement </render/cycles/nodes/types/vector/vector_displacement>` "
"node to the displacement output of the Material Output node. Procedural, "
"painted or baked textures can then be connected to these nodes."
msgstr ""

